            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Tutius Mani <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Dans</abbr><ex>ala</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>eq</abbr><ex>ues</ex></expan> ex <expan><abbr>co</abbr><ex>horte</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>IIII T&amp;lt;hr=RH&amp;gt;<expan><abbr>ac</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XXXV <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>st</abbr><ex>ipendiorum</ex></expan> X <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>posu</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>Bitus <expan><abbr>Stac</abbr><ex cert="low">i</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> ex <lb n="6"/>testamento 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Autopsie R. Wiegels. Inschriftfeld in Form einer tabula ansata. Oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes ein Reiter. Z. 1 (Ende), Z. 3 (Ende), Z. 4 (Ende): Der letzte Buchstabe steht jeweils ganz oder teilweise auf dem Rahmen oder rechts außerhalb der tabula ansata. (B): Boppert: Z. 3: XXV; Z. 4: sti(pendiorum).</p>
            </div>
